<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rube Collection - Luxurious Perfumes</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Lato:wght@300;400&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .heading-font {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }
        
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f0 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }
        
        .luxury-border {
            border: 2px solid #8b0000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white luxury-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
  
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-700 to-slate-800 py-8 px-6">
            <h1 class="heading-font text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center text-red-700 font-bold tracking-wide">
                Rube Collection
            </h1>
        </div>
        

        <div class="p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">

            <section>
                <h2 class="heading-font text-2xl text-red-800 font-semibold mb-3">Our Story</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    Rube Perfume was founded to bring luxurious perfumes that celebrate elegance and individuality. Each fragrance is carefully crafted using the finest ingredients to provide a premium and memorable experience.
                </p>
            </section>
       
            <section>
                <h2 class="heading-font text-2xl text-red-800 font-semibold mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    To offer high-quality perfumes that inspire confidence and delight the senses.
                </p>
            </section>
            

            <section>
                <h2 class="heading-font text-2xl text-red-800 font-semibold mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-700 mr-2">•</span>
                        <span>Premium Ingredients</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-700 mr-2">•</span>
                        <span>Long-Lasting Scents</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-700 mr-2">•</span>
                        <span>Authentic & Original Fragrances</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-red-700 mr-2">•</span>
                        <span>Exceptional Customer Service</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="heading-font text-2xl text-red-800 font-semibold mb-3">Explore Our Collection</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Discover our signature scents and find your perfect fragrance.
                </p>
                
                <div class="text-center">
                    <a href="/" class="bg-red-800 hover:bg-red-900 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                        Shop Now
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
        

        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-900 via-red-700 to-red-900"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>